Package org.hibernate.query.named

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NameableQuery
    Contract for Query impls that can be converted to a named query memento to be stored in the NamedQueryRepository
    NamedQueryMemento
    Named Query mementos are stored in the QueryEngine's NamedQueryRepository.
    NamedQueryMemento.ParameterMemento  
    NamedQueryProducer
    Specialization of NamedQueryMemento for mementos which can produce QueryImplementor implementations
    NamedQueryRepository  
    NamedResultSetMappingMemento
    Used to keep information about named result mappings defined by the application which can then be applied to native-sql and stored-procedure queries.
    RowReaderMemento
